info.title: EliteAPI
info.description: A backend API for https://elitebot.dev/ that provides Hypixel Skyblock data. Use of this API requires following the TOS. This API is not affiliated with Hypixel or Mojang.

get.summary: Get banned members from an event

post.summary: Ban a member from an event

delete.summary: Unban a member from an event

get.summary: Get a member of an event

parameters.name: days
parameters.description: Amount of days after the "from" time to include

parameters.name: from
parameters.description: Unix timestamp in seconds for the start of the data to return

parameters.name: perDay
parameters.description: Data points returned per 24 hour period

200.description: Returns the list of data points
